snippet.title: Aeon Wars Pre-Alpha GamePlay Trailer
snippet.description:
This video highlights the gameplay loop as well as the Collector Space of Aeon Wars: Maschinen Crisis. The state of the game is in pre-alpha and by far not complete. 

Join our Discord to follow our progress
 https://discord.gg/aGzKKQgNFv
